data.description: Well maintained canal front home in desirable Bayou Vista! This home features an open floor plan with tons of natural light and updates throughout. Two bedrooms and one full bath up, and one bedroom and full bath on the ground level. Catwalk is brand new and vinyl bulkhead was replaced in 2021 - this will last 25+ years! Upgrades also include new roof, electrical box and plumbing in 2018. Extended driveway to pull in an RV, boat or extra space to enjoy the outdoors. Watch the gorgeous sunsets from the upper deck, fish right from your property and have quick access to the bay! This home is great for entertaining or relaxing!
